com.google.gxp.compiler.base
Interface OutputLanguageVisitor<K,V>

Type Parameters:
K - parameter type for visitor
V - return type of visitor
public interface OutputLanguageVisitor<K,V>

Visitor for OutputLanguages. This interface deviates from the typical visitor interface in that the visit methods take a parameter other than the visited object. (the visited object is implied by the method)
